Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.24,0:23:45.21,Captions,,0000,0000,0000,,Executive Producer\NHENRY GOTO
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.27,0:23:47.24,Captions,,0000,0000,0000,,Producers\NSATOSHI FUJII, REIKO MATSUO\N& JONATHAN KLEIN
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.31,0:23:49.28,Captions,,0000,0000,0000,,Subtitlers\NBRETT JACOBSEN, DIANA TOLIN,\NAKI MATSUMOTO & MAKOTO SHIRAI
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.52,0:24:01.19,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,Imagine someone who is bold enough to\Nsteal a jewellery shop's diamond...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.19,0:24:02.66,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,in broad daylight.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.86,0:24:07.86,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, Professor Moriarty has done\Nexactly that... or so he thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.86,0:24:11.73,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,There was an unexpected hitch\Nto his seemingly perfect crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.34,0:24:16.69,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,If you ever find yourself in a mystery,\Nplease come see us at Baker Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.96,0:24:22.47,Ep Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Chaos!\NThe Doll Swap Case
